{"tid":2205720,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我覺得我條女比美容院呃錢","createTime":"2020-09-17T04:17:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T05:58:23.000Z","uid":127135,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"f819b512482437be511620ddb4a50a5ad692dfca","tid":2205720,"uid":127135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T04:17:48.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我條女廿尾近30歲 皮膚其實唔算好差<br />\n個樣都唔係差又唔係肥<br />\n收入算係比一般同齡嘅高D 又高過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢每個月都洗成$7000-$8000供比美容院<br />\n唔拿知佢買咗乜7 但聽佢講有facial有咩通淋巴有脫毛<br />\n雖然佢係自己俾錢冇問過我資助無叫過我比<br />\n但係大佬你諗吓<br />\n月供$8000 計落一年成十萬！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nP佢個K 諗起都肉赤 <br />\n但係佢唔覺得比人呃緊 仲覺得好值好抵<br />\n可以點叫佢收手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9152bcf3c04c6a240f8bf2001eac24ab3fc70fb7","tid":2205720,"uid":30379,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T04:20:21.000Z","msg":"佢整完皮膚好左靚左fit左受益人都係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b92acf2c1d04ff3500f9c729d9961245e7750e1d","tid":2205720,"uid":30379,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T04:21:17.000Z","msg":"同埋你有冇諗過佢做完,先有文中你對佢嘅評價"},{"pid":"a7b3b6d593bea7ea6b7c72d69ed68b7992c8361d","tid":2205720,"uid":321977,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T04:21:23.000Z","msg":"我就建議飛咗佢搵過個，咁蠢遲早再比人呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09c898aaa9384d672dd6ebccfd9b5229f57f0529","tid":2205720,"uid":276715,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T04:23:05.000Z","msg":"佢應該買左幾款package要長期供個隻 <br />\n又唔可以話呃嘅 係佢買得太多姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor